// Hero Section - Full viewport height
---

<section id="hero" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center text-center px-6">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl mb-8 text-stone-900 tracking-wide" style="font-weight: 200; line-height: 1.2;">
      Zenová meditácia v Košiciach
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-stone-700" style="font-weight: 300;">
      Súčasť medzinárodnej školy Kwan Um. Tradícia kórejského zenu.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-stone-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
